{"tid":681404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【女首富掃貨】$6,434萬澳洲豪宅神秘買家曝光？ 打破成交紀錄","createTime":"2018-05-28T04:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T07:11:07.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd3e4c844d18a5bcfe34af6a104695383b3a963","tid":681404,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【女首富掃貨】$6,434萬澳洲豪宅神秘買家曝光？ 打破成交紀錄</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180528&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58243502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180528%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58243502&d=jVfVKlZMpNPP2cvnjC5RPl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9563f30a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180528%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58243502&h=b8b49e41\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180528&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58243502</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527428237_e4ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527428237_e4ac.jpg&h=77ee65e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人全球買買買，尤其喜歡買樓。近日，澳洲悉尼的Hills District一棟佔地1,200平方米、有7間睡房，配備泳池、Spa設施、網球場、馬厩、菜園等的豪宅，以1,085萬澳元（下同，約6,434萬港元）成交，比當地的成交價高逾200萬元（約1,186萬港元），打破悉尼市郊住宅的成交紀錄，買家身份一直神秘，至昨日有澳洲媒體報道，買家是被稱為「白手興家」的新晉女首富周群飛及她的丈夫鄭俊龍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433845_2dd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433845_2dd6.jpg&h=77cd1189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>豪宅大門極具氣派。</em><br />\n<br />\n澳洲媒體Domain昨日報道，這間豪宅傳由周群飛丈夫鄭俊龍登記，已經得到外國投資審查委員會（FIRB）的批准。《福布斯》顯示，周群飛創辦的藍思科技（Lens Technology）目前有8.2萬名員工，公司估值約114億美元（約889億港元）。報道指周群飛是個工作狂，在澳洲購買豪宅相信是用作度假屋使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433846_5652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433846_5652.jpg&h=bfbe657e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>豪宅佔地廣闊，包括泳池、網球場。</em><br />\n<br />\n傳由周群飛購入的豪宅名為Moncur Estate，位於Hills District的Dural，距離悉尼市中心約36公里，建於2012年。當地房地產資料顯示，這棟由沙岩為主要建築材料的豪宅，由前業主蓋伊（David Guy）和他的妻子積奇（Jackie）建造，兩人在去年11月將豪宅出租，每星期租金4,995元（約29,622港元），隨後又交予地產經紀放盤。據報，當時這物業叫價1,095萬元（約6,494萬港元），周群飛與丈夫則是在今年4月13日完成交易。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433847_9d00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433847_9d00.jpg&h=dd613a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>花園內的泳池是其中一個賣點。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433848_38f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433848_38f2.jpg&h=f8fbee8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>走入大門，是裝修具氣派的大廳。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433851_18b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433851_18b5.jpg&h=ed24e4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>屋內有開放式客廳。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433852_0661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433852_0661.jpg&h=245d79fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>廚房內空間巨大，不少位置都使用大理石。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527433853_18f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527433853_18f4.jpg&h=1c3e001e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>主人浴室內有水晶燈。</em><br />\n<br />\n曾經參觀這間豪宅的地產經紀，都對這棟法式鄉村風格物業讚不絕口：「這豪宅實在讓人驚艷，是看過最好的物業！」「具規模又夠隱私，整體感覺很好！」豪宅擁有華麗客廳、桌球房、家庭劇院，設有冷藏室的大理石廚房，及現化代的智能家居設備。屋內7個睡房均設有獨立浴室，主人套房更有獨立私人露台及衣帽間。豪宅範圍內更有修剪整齊的花園，內設15米長泳池、水療設施、網球場、馬厩、菜園、遊樂區和6車位車房。<br />\n悉尼一直都吸引不少中國人在當地置業，Dural更是中國富豪的新目標，今年1月當地一棟豪宅，由譯音劉英霞（Yingxia Liu）和葉雲秀（Yunshou Ye）購入，成交價880萬元（約5,218萬港元），當時打破成交紀錄，沒想到這紀錄只維持約2個月便被打破。<br />\n對於澳洲媒體的報道，放盤的地產代理不予置評，但鄭俊龍的律師則否認周群飛與鄭俊龍是買家。<br />\n澳洲Domain/<a href=\"http://realestate.com.au\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frealestate.com.au&d=jVfVKlZMpNPP2cvnjC5RPl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b1d50a81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">realestate.com.au</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180528/58243502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58243502&d=jVfVKlZMpNPP2cvnjC5RPl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2c09a68a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58243502&h=a07b923a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180528/58243502</a>"},{"pid":"18a921d79524873fe183ec95fe832e5136f01a28","tid":681404,"uid":7821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"6千幾萬就打破紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4a001f6289dd5e5ecfafce7444c27a761d582a","tid":681404,"uid":61586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"區區6000幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵屌啦"},{"pid":"1dafda3f21d109f34ba6400647a5af1755007b13","tid":681404,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4a001f6289dd5e5ecfafce7444c27a761d582a","tid":681404,"uid":61586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"區區6000幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵屌啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"買買買"},{"pid":"7cc911f2604580b4e5c794c95072937bf482feb2","tid":681404,"uid":135957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b80c67f3e04ea5371a6be12407036cf2045e7fd","tid":681404,"uid":132941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"咁都破紀錄？Sydney Cremorne Mosman 地區大把千幾萬澳紙嘅屋，使唔使上晒新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1fd78b75db681337726e21c838e5e4e38d6d24","tid":681404,"uid":117628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"成萬2萬3呎，一億都唔洗<br />\n係香港一千呎都已經成千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb7ca11794a67f56f680085d7fcda3db6bb2628","tid":681404,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"香港1億買唔買咁嘅盤"},{"pid":"19eb99cde09d19e538a72ecdc8353ec52978e173","tid":681404,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"香港錢用嚟買香港樓完全唔值"},{"pid":"9f5a7534cc8e127334b12bf108e7cbc8dc91dcc4","tid":681404,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"當地紀錄啫，上面班友咁都要拎香港樓價打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}